    "It is worth noting that this method requires labeled data for model training, making it a supervised task, which differs from our settings.",
    "Query 1 Answer 1.... Query n Answer n Query Q A* Embedding Model Average Few shot Query-Answer Answer 1 Query 1.... Answer n Query n Answer A* Few shot Answer-Query Repeat K times (1) (2) (3) Cosine Similarity Q Embedding Vector 1 2 k Embedding Vector Figure 1: An illustration of the InterrogateLLM method.",
    "(1) A few-shot prompt and a query are fed into F LLM, which generates an answer.",
